---
/**
 * Terminal mockup component inspired by carbon.now.sh
 * Shows realistic Fastmail MCP interactions as a hero visual
 */
---

<div class="terminal-wrapper">
  <div class="terminal">
    <!-- Title bar with traffic lights -->
    <div class="terminal-titlebar">
      <div class="terminal-dots">
        <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
      </div>
      <span class="terminal-title">fastmail-mcp — zsh — 120×48</span>
      <div class="terminal-dots invisible">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span class="dot"></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terminal body -->
    <div class="terminal-body">
      <pre><code><span class="prompt">❯</span> <span class="cmd">claude</span> <span class="arg">"Check my inbox for anything urgent"</span>

<span class="dim">Using fastmail search_emails tool...</span>

<span class="accent">Inbox — 3 unread</span>

  <span class="badge badge-flag">★</span> <span class="sender">Alice Park</span>  <span class="subject">Q2 Budget Final Approval Needed</span>  <span class="dim">10:42 AM</span>
  <span class="badge badge-new">●</span> <span class="sender">GitHub</span>  <span class="subject">[fastmail-mcp] New issue #47</span>  <span class="dim"> 9:15 AM</span>
  <span class="badge badge-new">●</span> <span class="sender">David Chen</span>  <span class="subject">Flight itinerary for Tokyo trip</span>  <span class="dim"> 8:30 AM</span>

<span class="prompt">❯</span> <span class="cmd">claude</span> <span class="arg">"Reply to Alice — approved, cc finance team"</span>

<span class="dim">Using fastmail reply_to_email tool...</span>
<span class="success">✓</span> <span class="text">Reply sent to </span><span class="accent">alice.park@company.com</span>
  <span class="dim">CC:</span> <span class="text">finance-team@company.com</span>
  <span class="dim">Re:</span> <span class="text">Q2 Budget Final Approval Needed</span>

<span class="prompt">❯</span> <span class="cmd">claude</span> <span class="arg">"Move the GitHub notification to my Dev folder"</span>

<span class="dim">Using fastmail move_email tool...</span>
<span class="success">✓</span> <span class="text">Moved to </span><span class="accent">Dev/GitHub</span>

<span class="prompt">❯</span> <span class="cmd">claude</span> <span class="arg">"Find David's phone number"</span>

<span class="dim">Using fastmail search_contacts tool...</span>

  <span class="text">David Chen</span>
  <span class="dim">Email:</span>  <span class="accent">david.chen@company.com</span>
  <span class="dim">Phone:</span>  <span class="text">(415) 555-0198</span>

<span class="prompt">❯</span> <span class="cursor">▌</span></code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .terminal-wrapper {
    perspective: 1000px;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .terminal {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06),
      0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6),
      0 0 80px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.08);
    transform: rotateX(2deg);
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
  }

  .terminal:hover {
    transform: rotateX(0deg);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08),
      0 30px 60px -15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
      0 0 120px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.12);
  }

  .terminal-titlebar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: #2a2a2a;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
  }

  .terminal-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .terminal-dots.invisible {
    visibility: hidden;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot-red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot-yellow { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot-green { background: #28c840; }

  .terminal-title {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .terminal-body pre {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  .terminal-body code {
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .prompt { color: #f97316; font-weight: 600; }
  .cmd { color: #60a5fa; }
  .arg { color: #fbbf24; }
  .dim { color: #555; }
  .accent { color: #f97316; }
  .text { color: #e5e5e5; }
  .success { color: #34d399; font-weight: 700; }

  .sender {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 20ch;
    color: #e5e5e5;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .subject {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 34ch;
    color: #a3a3a3;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 1.5ch;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .badge-flag { color: #fbbf24; }
  .badge-new { color: #f97316; }

  .cursor {
    color: #f97316;
    animation: blink 1.2s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .terminal-body pre {
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .terminal-body {
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .terminal-title {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
